Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and captivating image depicting the omnipresence of God in a way that visually represents His infinite nature. Consider depicting a vast, cosmic landscape with shimmering stars and swirling galaxies to symbolize God's presence transcending time and place. Incorporate subtle, divine light emanating from every corner of the universe, illustrating the concept of God being present everywhere simultaneously. The image should evoke a sense of awe and wonder, inviting viewers to contemplate the boundless nature of God's presence in a visually stunning and spiritually uplifting manner.
